    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it in pristine shape\u2014no scratches, a spotless interior, and it still drives like a total dream. If you're looking for a car that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
