    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem of a car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s basically like new! It\u2019s been kept in a garage and pampered since day one\u2014no scratches, no weird smells, just that fresh car feeling every time you step inside. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and is ready for a new home, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
