      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe in Alpine White. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system for peak volumetric efficiency. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been meticulously addressed: the rear subframe has been reinforced, rod bearings replaced with VAC-coated units, and the VANOS system overhauled with Beisan components. The chassis remains rigid with zero oxidation, and the suspension maintains factory-spec damping and bushing integrity. All electronics are fully operational with no pixel failure. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the serious collector.",
